Package: quartoRenderAddin
Type: Package
Title: Render Current Quarto Document Without Preview Server
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rob", "Cavanaugh", email = "rb-cavanaugh@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An RStudio addin that renders the currently open .qmd/.Rmd
    file to HTML and opens it in the browser, without starting a
    background preview server or file watcher.
